### Ready
Fired when the peer is fully initialized and has its own ID.

```js
peer.on('ready', (id) => {
  // your peer id
})
```

### Connection Request
Fired when another peer tries to connect to you.

```js
peer.on('connection-request', ({ id }) => {
  // decide to accept or reject
})
```

- id: requesting peer id
